{"tid":2249270,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中藍水炮投訴一年無果  毛漢促查警暴：令青年見未來","createTime":"2020-10-19T08:34:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T08:42:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03cd09f4c74ef40d7ad2e0ad73ad52bbc6274770","tid":2249270,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:34:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/7XLNKMD4H5CUHHGBGZM2GNJOOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2F7XLNKMD4H5CUHHGBGZM2GNJOOI%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=b6560b29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2F7XLNKMD4H5CUHHGBGZM2GNJOOI%2F&h=4bb0dfb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/7XLNKMD4H5CUHHGBGZM2GNJOOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中藍水炮投訴一年無果 <br />\n毛漢促查警暴：令青年見未來<br />\n<br />\n警暴經常「揚威」國際，去年10月中警方以藍色水炮噴射尖沙嘴清真寺一幕在網絡廣傳，當中包括印度協會前主席毛漢褚簡寧（Mohan Chugani）全身染藍的畫面。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。土生土長70多年的他，強調自己非藍或黃，只是希望香港變回一個令年輕人有未來的地方，原因很簡單，「我梗係關心我屋企」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：轟軟弱政府以警武裝 「香港要換血」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，多次向清真寺發射具刺激性藍色水炮，毛漢當時在寺前與友人寒暄亦慘被染藍，警方事後罕有地在facebook專頁聲稱「誤中」清真寺。<br />\n<br />\n記者訪問當日，與毛漢重返現場，他示範當時背向水炮，如何用力緊握欄杆以免跌倒，「醫生同我講，好彩你冇（正面）對住佢，如果唔係眼珠都甩埋；中咗時成身好似着咗火，又睇唔到嘢，成粒鐘都睇唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/p8TCHlAYTpWcPyIi8cqAn_IOr5o=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NBEM4NLQMJFVDLT3X4U5HFW2JY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fp8TCHlAYTpWcPyIi8cqAn_IOr5o%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNBEM4NLQMJFVDLT3X4U5HFW2JY.jpg&h=14adb233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■毛漢本來會在清真寺外乘巴士回家，惟事發後一度不敢再行經寺外。<br />\n<br />\n水炮之痛，後遺未斷。毛漢指至今雙腳。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n投訴一年未果，。。。。。。。。。。。。。，「大家嘥咗成年時間，個結果係乜先得㗎？證據就畀晒你。」究竟警方發射水炮時有否做錯，他覺得事實已很清晰，「如果唔係，當日特首就唔會同我道歉，一哥都唔會同我道歉啦。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zKG28raodj3T6WXlfquP0NUcL0E=/830x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A6GTV5GK4JBFTEHE3763DSQUQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FzKG28raodj3T6WXlfquP0NUcL0E%3D%2F830x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA6GTV5GK4JBFTEHE3763DSQUQM.jpg&h=b3c96781&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■當日毛漢被水炮射至全身染藍，皮膚感刺痛亦無法張開眼。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3Q5kz__gwkjMZApWPFXFPK40vqI=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KZNIVH5FBFBOPFQSVJH6V7ROVI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3Q5kz__gwkjMZApWPFXFPK40vqI%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKZNIVH5FBFBOPFQSVJH6V7ROVI.jpg&h=72b5dcc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年10月20日九龍大遊行，警方出動水炮車，沿彌敦道推進期間多次向清真寺發射藍色水炮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Rr7XHkirmVAAf9Cj_8zM7-29yPA=/2048x1365/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/32UUAFWYSFBYLCUTKNMD54LJOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRr7XHkirmVAAf9Cj_8zM7-29yPA%3D%2F2048x1365%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F32UUAFWYSFBYLCUTKNMD54LJOM.jpg&h=04e6f34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■毛漢一年前到警總投訴，惟調查至今仍未有結果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你話唔查，咁唔通警方乜都冇錯，冚把冷都係hero？冇可能。」<br />\n<br />\n事件沉澱過後，他認為政府處理手法很有問題，沒有考慮被射中人士要如何治理等等，而且水劑成份至今未明。毛漢強調政府必須成立獨立調查委員會徹查警暴，「你話唔做調查，咁唔通成個警方乜都冇做錯，冚把冷都係hero？呢個係冇可能嘅事；後生仔你話犯法咪拉佢，但有冇重手咗呢？可能有，咁就公開查啦，獨立咁查。」<br />\n<br />\n他指社會較一年前呈兩極，例如其家中掛滿與歷屆特首合照卻獨缺林鄭，「Carrie我同佢有好多相，但係有時有朋友上嚟會問，Why did you take a picture with her？」他指和朋友見面並非為政治爭論，因此便沒有掛上合照，笑指「例如我細佬上嚟見到（合照），佢第一個「『媽』我呀！」<br />\n<br />\n要修補關係，他認為當局要主動與年輕人溝通，「唔係我哋幾廿歲，始終令到香港青年失望或者要移民，都係對香港係無益。」在香港生活逾半個世紀，他說1997年臨近回歸時期，港人同樣非常擔心未來，他清楚記得當年6月30號晚大雨滂沱，「望住電視睇住落旗再升五星旗，我坐喺梳化度流眼淚，真係有！話無嗰個就呃你嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n回歸後數年好像一切如初，但慢慢便開始轉變，例如教育方針強調愛國等。毛漢覺得每個人也應該愛國，但如果不喜歡國家制度，人們會嘗試改變，有些官員過份強調愛國只會適得其反，「唔講好過講」，應順其自然。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「Fear can rule，但我都話，你唔可以kill一個dream。」<br />\n<br />\n回顧港英政府管治風格，他形容港英視香港為一個快樂大家庭，「當時人口五、六百萬，中文有句餓你唔死，食你唔飽，但總之會照顧你，當時人哋窮都窮得好開心，但𠵱家啲人窮係唔開心。」他認為是因為缺失了某種東西，亦可能是管治風格不同，不少在港印度人亦正考慮移民，「40幾50歲嗰啲，真係諗緊去美國或者其他亞洲國家，例如馬來西亞、菲律賓，最多人想去新加坡。」<br />\n<br />\n毛漢部份家人已移民美國，但他依然留在香港，「我係香港人，我梗係關心我屋企。」他多次強調自己不是「黃或藍」，只是一心想香港好，呼籲更多「middle party（中間派）」站出來講真心說話，指現時是最適合時機，「Come on！Do something！得我一個講係無用。」。。。。。。。。，「Fear can rule，（但）我都話，你唔可以kill一個dream。」"},{"pid":"d61a769851d5d8545f2b0e98f7afdc367e30c85b","tid":2249270,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:38:50.000Z","msg":"留名等睇最後話誤會 冇人要負責"},{"pid":"526f14ec7dda3d9471f754ab111305382b303436","tid":2249270,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e1e642201e1ccddc5fcf081658dd2408e4db2f","tid":2249270,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:41:31.000Z","msg":"實攬隻狗 唔洗諗"},{"pid":"06c7ec15a2e21a62f1c4dff01fe356795f6461e9","tid":2249270,"uid":19062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:41:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />印度人<br />\n可以拎去搞外交"},{"pid":"9f2c97e8e8ce6e571d6753d1c80ada91493e3ee9","tid":2249270,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"咪道咗歉囉，你唔係想要皇軍交人頭比你啊？張建宗都唔敢出聲，你邊位啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}